que gravitational wave signature, which will allow a decisive\nidentification in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2012 21:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Nov 2012 20:59:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-11-22"}
