A that was never directly detected. We\nsuggest that photoionization can play an important dynamical role in shaping\nthe ring nebula, and we speculate that this might help explain the origin of\nthe polar rings around SN1987A. abridged.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2012 22:29:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Nov 2012 06:00:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
