namics with the benefit of fewer (integer) variables and\nless potential traffic holding. The proposed MILP explicitly captures vehicle\nspillback, avoids traffic holding, and simultaneously minimizes travel delay\nand addresses emission-related concerns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2012 23:37:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jun 2014 11:31:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2016 12:35:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-25"}
